OL,3,C'It is like a wave of grief' parent
OL,4,Cdescribes how it feels to lose Zoe's
OL,5,CPlace
OL,7,FVideo Report by Anna Youssef
OL,9,FFour-year-old Jude has a rare genetic
OL,10,Fcondition and attends classes at Zoe's
OL,11,Fplace, his needs are so complex he
OL,12,Fwouldn't be able to attend any other
OL,13,Fkind of school but his classroom is
OL,14,Fabout to close for good.
OL,16,FZoe's Place is one of only three
OL,17,Fhospices in the UK specialising in
OL,18,Fbabies and children under five. It
OL,19,Foffers respite and end-of-life care
OL,20,Fand supports the whole family.
