OL,5,CPlace
OL,7,FIt was announced that the hospice
OL,8,Fwould have to shut its doors by the
OL,9,Fend of the year after plans to move to
OL,10,Fa new purpose-built building fell
OL,11,Fthrough.
OL,13,FNow Zoe's Place has until the end of
OL,14,FOctober to raise the #5 million to
OL,15,Fbuild a new facility.
