OL,3,C'It is like a wave of grief' parent
OL,4,Cdescribes how it feels to lose Zoe's
OL,5,CPlace
OL,7,FJude's mum Eberley Pines is his carer,
OL,8,Fshe was shocked by the announcement of
OL,9,Fclosure "When we got that call on
OL,10,FMonday I felt like someone had just
OL,11,Ftold me that someone had lost their
OL,12,Flife because it is like a wave of
OL,13,Fgrief, If Zoe's wasn't here I don't
OL,14,Fknow what the future would hold for
OL,15,Fhis care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
