OL,3,C'It is like a wave of grief' parent
OL,4,Cdescribes how it feels to lose Zoe's
OL,5,CPlace
OL,7,F"They don't just care for Jude they
OL,8,Fcare for us as a whole family. We just
OL,9,Fpray that the service stays here
OL,10,Fbecause it is needed for the now and
OL,11,Fit is needed for the future children
OL,12,Fas well."
OL,14,FThe announcement also means 41 staff
OL,15,Fnow face losing their jobs but they
OL,16,Fsay their main concern is for the
OL,17,Ffamilies and patients.
OL,19,FThere are just 17 days left to raise 5
OL,20,Fmillion pounds to save the specialist
OL,21,Fbaby hospice Zoe's Place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
