OL,7,FThey said, "As a Liverpool-born
OL,8,Fbusiness we will always give back to
OL,9,Four community and we hope this
OL,10,Fcontribution helps keep the doors
OL,11,Fopen."
OL,13,FThe hospice say the current situation
OL,14,Fis caused by the cost of living crisis.
