OL,7,FMatt Meaney- head of fundraising at
OL,8,FZoe's Place said: "As an organisation,
OL,9,Four expertise is looking after sick
OL,10,Fkids. Its not building buildings or
OL,11,Fdeveloping buildings and I think
OL,12,Feverything took a lot longer than we
OL,13,Fexpected and the economy has not
OL,14,Fhelped us either.
