OL,5,CPlace
OL,7,F"Everybody knows the cost of living
OL,8,Fhas gone through the roof, inflation
OL,9,Fhas gone through the roof and the cost
OL,10,Fof our project went up and the cost of
OL,11,Frunning a hospice is continuing to
OL,12,Frise so everything has taken longer
OL,13,Fand cost more than we expected."
